original_title: Muse: Live at KAABOO Del Mar Festival 2017
overview: Muse were one of the headliners of the festival alongside Red Hot Chili Peppers, P!nk and Tom Petty & the Heartbreakers. Muse closed the day on Saturday, taking the stage after Jane's Addiction.  Performed: 16th September 2017
title: Muse: Live at KAABOO Del Mar Festival 2017
